Package: fsdac
Title: Robust Data Analysis through monitoring
Version: 0.5-21
Date: 2021-08-04
VersionNote: Released ... on CRAN
Authors@R: c(person("Valentin", "Todorov", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "valentin@todorov.at", comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4215-0245"))
         , person("Aldo", "Corbellini", role = "aut", email = "aldo.corbellini@unipr.it")
         , person("Marco",  "Riani", role = "aut", email = "marco.riani@unipr.it")
